Go through the playbook it has all the options.

But make sure that the hosts/Inventory file look like this for all the examples to work seamlessly.



[main]
rhel-server ansible_connection=local ## Variable at host level -- HOSTVARS

[centos]
centos1 ansible_port=22

[ubuntu]
centos2 ansible_become=false

[centos:vars]
ansible_user=root

## till above is the proper host file for testing out the scenarios in the playbook. Anythig new add below